Package: regDIF
Title: Regularized Differential Item Functioning
Version: 0.0.1
Author: William Belzak
Maintainer: William Belzak <wbelzak@live.unc.edu>
Description: Performs regularization of differential item functioning (DIF) in item response theory (IRT) and confirmatory factor analysis (CFA) models using a penalized expectation-maximization algorithm.
